sections.heading: Eligibility for insurance
description: We specialize in providing insurance to current, former and retired military members, their spouses, current and retired. Department of Defense employees and children of current or former AFI members.
However, we can still be your agent and provide you with quotes from our partners if you do not fall into one of these categories.

options.label: Military (active duty, former / separated / retired / disabled, surviving spouse)
Current or Retired Department of Defense Employee
Child of current or former Armed Forces Insurance member
Non-military (We can provide you with quotes from our partners)

sections.heading: Save Your Quote
description: This email will be used to send you a link to finish your quote at a later time.

fields.label: Provide us with your email address.

sections.heading: Product Unvailable
description: We don't currently offer insurance in your area.
If you have questions about our coverage areas and would like to talk with an agent please call 1-800-495-8234.

sections.heading: We will contact you as soon as we have your quote ready
sections.disclaimer: To offer you an accurate quote and/or policy, we (AFI and AFI affiliates) may collect information from consumer reporting agencies, such as credit history. Future reports may be used to update or renew your insurance. By completing this quote, you agree to receive marketing materials from Armed Forces Insurance. You can request removal at any time. Please review our Privacy Policy - Information Gathering.
